data.description:
Beautiful executive brick, pool home in park like setting located in the ''lake area'' of Keystone Heights, Fl. ( New roof to be installed soon)
 Inground  pool with screened enclosure boast an outside lanai with an amazing wood-burning brick fireplace. The perfect location to entertain friends and family or enjoy the serenity of your own oasis. There is an attached two car garage as well. The home has an open floor plan with hardwood floors. the living room has a gas fireplace and French doors (with pool exit alarm). The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and beautiful solid granite countertops, with breakfast bar & breakfast nook area. This open floor plan offers a formal dining room/ office. Amazing master suite is highlighted with a gas fireplace for a cozy atmosphere.The home has plenty of extras, A must see!!!
